## Phase ↔ version mapping

- `0.1.x` → Phase 0–1 (Tools + Streamable HTTP + Server Card).
- `0.2.x` → Phase 2 (Prompts).
- `0.3.x` → Phase 3 (Form elicitation).
- `0.4.x` → Phase 4 (URL elicitation + OAuth).
- `0.5.x` → Phase 5 (MCP Apps UI).
- `1.0.0` → public surface frozen under SemVer.

